FT  01 NOV 94 / UK Company News: BPT/Harborne
Bradford Property Trust has increased its offer for Harborne Tenants from
230p to 260p per share, valuing the property investment company at Pounds
12.9m.
Harborne shareholders may elect to receive new BPT shares instead of all or
part of the cash offer on the basis of 140 new BPT shares for every Pounds
260 payable under the offer.
They may also elect to receive Pounds 1 nominal of BPT loan notes for every
Pounds 1 cash entitlement. Other conditions, including the preference offer,
are unchanged.
The increased offer follows information relating to the recent revaluation
of Harborne's properties.
